Package assignment.planetai

Class PlanetaryBody

java.lang.Object
assignment.planetai.PlanetaryBody
All Implemented Interfaces:
edu.ccri.assignment.planets.data.DataAccessElement
Direct Known Subclasses:
DwarfPlanet, Moon, Planet
public abstract class PlanetaryBody extends Object implements edu.ccri.assignment.planets.data.DataAccessElement
This class represents a planetary body.

A planetary body has the following attributes:
  • name
  • classification
  • diameter
  • weight ratio to earth
  • distance from earth
  • distance from the sun
  • orbital eccentricity
  • albedo
  • day length
  • year length
  • drag coefficient
  • orbital velocity
